                        *** Release Information *** 
  
    Game Notes:
    ~~~~~~~~~~~

    Go to war in all-new single-player and multiplayer campaigns that take you
    from the searing heat of North Africa to the treacherous mountains of
    Italy. Overcome overwhelming odds and the brutal terrain to emerge
    victorious in this explosive addition to the MOHAA experience.


    Game Features:
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    
    - Eleven single-player levels ranging from the fight for Kasserine Pass in
    North Africa to the historic battle of Monte Battaglia in the heart of
    Italy.
    - Nine new multiplayer levels including the monastery at Monte Cassino,
    the streets of Messina, and the beach at Anzio.
    - Improved multiplayer battles, including the all-new Liberation mode in
    which defeated players become POWs who must be rescued by their teammates.
    Plus the popular Tug-of-War and Objective modes.
    - Access to historically accurate World War II era weapons.
    - Enter and exit vehicles at will including the M4 Sherman Tank.
    - New soldier models, skins and voices, including American, British and
    Italian troops.
    - Sound effects by the award winning Medal of HonorT sound design team at
    EALA.
